46:14.898 --> 46:17.025
How are you feeling?

46:17.192 --> 46:20.237
Like fat man
shit in my head.

46:20.404 --> 46:22.072
What happened?

46:22.239 --> 46:26.452
Well, you fainted,
but everything's fine now.

46:26.618 --> 46:28.412
Why it's night?

46:28.579 --> 46:30.205
Oh, you've been out
for quite a while.

46:30.372 --> 46:32.332
I recommend you see
your physician

46:32.499 --> 46:35.377
and have him test you
for narcolepsy.

46:48.640 --> 46:50.851
Is there something
you want to tell me?

46:53.270 --> 46:55.063
Most folks start with
how long it's been

46:55.230 --> 46:57.024
since their last confession.

47:00.235 --> 47:02.613
I'm not here for that.

47:02.779 --> 47:04.948
Then why are you here?

47:05.991 --> 47:07.951
I just needed a sounding board.

47:08.118 --> 47:09.745
I've already been to a bar

47:09.912 --> 47:12.623
and my favourite hooker is down
with a case of the clap, so...

47:12.789 --> 47:15.125
I'm the next best thing.

47:15.292 --> 47:17.127
Something like that, yeah.

47:21.673 --> 47:24.176
I'm about to do things
I don't want to.

47:25.302 --> 47:27.846
God gave you free will.
You have a choice.

47:29.264 --> 47:31.141
God?

47:32.142 --> 47:34.019
Yeah.

47:34.186 --> 47:37.856
As far as choice,
I don't get one.

47:40.692 --> 47:43.111
Sooner or later
I'm going to have to give in.

47:43.278 --> 47:46.365
It's gonna be ugly
and I'll have to live with it.

47:48.075 --> 47:51.745
Not that it matters, but I
assume you're not of the faith.

47:53.080 --> 47:55.249
You could tell?

47:55.415 --> 47:57.334
But you do seem to be
carrying guilt.

47:57.501 --> 47:59.336
I'm guessing
the reason you're here,

47:59.503 --> 48:02.464
even though
you're a nonbeliever, is because

48:02.631 --> 48:05.634
you're hoping for some kind of
pre-emptive absolution

48:05.801 --> 48:07.511
for the sins
you're about to commit.

48:07.678 --> 48:10.222
It doesn't work like that.

48:11.932 --> 48:13.725
Why not?

48:14.726 --> 48:17.938
I'm sorry. I can't help you.

48:24.987 --> 48:26.780
No-one can.

49:36.141 --> 49:39.186
You're not going to go
all bridezilla on me, are you?

49:39.353 --> 49:42.564
You kidding? I am easy-peasy.

49:44.524 --> 49:46.860
But it is the most important day
of my life.

49:47.027 --> 49:51.948
Any girl's, really,
so I want it to be right.

49:52.115 --> 49:53.909
Of course.

49:54.910 --> 49:56.912
The flower arrangements
need to have

49:57.079 --> 50:01.500
six 12-inch white Macedonian
roses - one red, three yellow.

50:01.667 --> 50:05.128
The reception is going to be
a five-course meal,

50:05.295 --> 50:07.673
sit-down for 300
with place cards.

50:07.839 --> 50:09.883
- I hate open seating.
- 300...

50:10.050 --> 50:13.136
And we're going to write
all of our own vows, of course.

50:13.303 --> 50:14.930
How soon can you get yours
to me?

50:15.097 --> 50:16.890
Because I need to have it
carved into granite

50:17.057 --> 50:18.850
for a wall plaque
to put over the fireplace

50:19.017 --> 50:22.813
just as a reminder of all the
promises that you made to me.

50:27.317 --> 50:30.028
I'm just fucking with you.

50:32.364 --> 50:34.366
You looked like
you were going to cry.

50:34.533 --> 50:36.410
I was.

50:37.452 --> 50:40.205
No, honestly, all I ask
is that you wear a suit.

50:40.372 --> 50:43.750
I want to see what you look like
dressed up, just once.

50:43.917 --> 50:47.003
I think I can accommodate you
on that.

50:48.046 --> 50:51.675
And kids. I want kids.

50:53.885 --> 50:57.472
We'll live in a beautiful house
by the ocean.

50:57.639 --> 51:00.350
Maybe have another getaway
in the mountains.

51:01.351 --> 51:04.187
And a couple Ducatis, of course.

51:05.647 --> 51:08.275
OK, if we're going to live large
and support a family,

51:08.442 --> 51:10.318
you're going to need to step up
your game.

51:11.570 --> 51:13.405
I already have.

51:30.672 --> 51:32.591
What are you doing?

51:32.758 --> 51:35.343
Uh, just giving you guys
some space.

51:35.510 --> 51:38.221
- Roman's got room, so...
- No way.

51:38.388 --> 51:41.057
Just because I'm engaged doesn't
mean you have to move out.

51:42.642 --> 51:44.686
You need to make your own life.

51:44.853 --> 51:46.897
It's time for you to be happy.
You deserve it.

51:47.063 --> 51:48.940
So do you.

51:53.069 --> 51:54.863
He does make you happy, right?

51:58.116 --> 52:00.368
Yeah.

52:00.535 --> 52:02.370
Good.

52:04.623 --> 52:06.458
You know...

52:07.876 --> 52:12.047
..wherever I am,
you'll always be welcome.

52:15.967 --> 52:17.969
Ride or die, cuz.

52:19.638 --> 52:21.473
Ride or die.

52:24.643 --> 52:27.646
My other favourite Rumancek.

52:27.813 --> 52:29.648
Oh, no.
Negative on the naked man hugs.

52:29.815 --> 52:31.942
We're family now. It's fine.
Come on.

52:32.108 --> 52:34.319
OK.

52:34.486 --> 52:36.321
Hey, can you give me a ride
to the warehouse?

52:36.488 --> 52:38.323
I need to see my uncle,
bike's in the shop.

52:38.490 --> 52:40.242
Fine, just put some pants on,
for God's sakes.

52:40.408 --> 52:42.202
OK.

52:54.548 --> 52:57.175
In all the excitement I forgot
to ask, how'd it go with the PI?

52:57.342 --> 52:58.969
Any news about Miranda?

52:59.135 --> 53:01.179
When I hear something,
I'll let you know.

53:05.934 --> 53:08.103
It's just frustrating, you know.

53:09.437 --> 53:11.606
Yeah. I get it.

53:13.733 --> 53:16.695
So I found some new buyers.

53:16.862 --> 53:18.738
They're willing to pay 1.7.

53:18.905 --> 53:20.657
You're shitting me!

53:20.824 --> 53:24.077
My brother,
I shit you not.

53:25.078 --> 53:26.705
And the best part,

53:26.872 --> 53:30.041
you and I are going to get
200,000 off the top.

53:31.209 --> 53:35.672
So...we're running game
on our own people?

53:35.839 --> 53:37.591
It's a finder's fee.

53:37.757 --> 53:40.927
We'll all be splitting
1.5 million instead of 1.2.

53:41.094 --> 53:43.221
I brokered the deal.
No-one knows the difference.

53:43.388 --> 53:46.224
- Everyone wins.
- So who are the buyers?

53:46.391 --> 53:49.060
An organisation
out of Pottstown.

53:52.564 --> 53:55.150
The Croatians are the only ones
who operate out of there.

53:58.445 --> 54:00.196
Shit.

54:00.363 --> 54:04.075
Andreas, you cannot fuck
with those people.

54:04.242 --> 54:06.661
If anything goes sideways, they
will ass-rape us with ice picks.

54:06.828 --> 54:08.580
I've got it handled.

54:09.581 --> 54:11.207
You do want your future nieces
and nephews

54:11.374 --> 54:13.168
to go to private school,
don't you?

54:17.339 --> 54:19.132
You gotta trust me.

54:20.717 --> 54:23.845
I'm the guy who saved your life,
remember?

54:31.895 --> 54:34.189
I swear to God, Andreas,
if anything goes...

54:34.356 --> 54:36.483
- I could kiss you on the mouth right...
- Don't!

54:38.693 --> 54:42.322
You do know you've got intimacy
issues, right?

55:26.199 --> 55:29.452
You! What the fuck was that?

55:42.382 --> 55:44.175
Don't!

55:55.228 --> 55:57.022
Who are you?

56:00.400 --> 56:02.444
My name is Annie...

56:03.528 --> 56:05.613
..and I am just like you.

56:14.164 --> 56:17.542
♪ I have to have you

56:20.378 --> 56:23.089
♪ I've got it bad

56:26.801 --> 56:30.055
♪ If I can't have you

56:32.682 --> 56:36.061
♪ Then no-one can

56:39.606 --> 56:42.901
♪ I've got a desperate heart

56:43.068 --> 56:48.156
♪ I don't know if this is love

56:48.323 --> 56:49.991
♪ But I have to have you. ♪

